  "excerpt": "The Five Dysfunctions of a Team reveals the root causes of team failure through a compelling leadership fable. Using the fictional Decisionogan Corporation as a vehicle, Patrick Lencioni builds a five-level pyramid of dysfunction — from absence of trust at the base, through fear of conflict, lack of commitment, avoidance of accountability, to inattention to results at the apex — and shows how overcoming each layer creates genuinely cohesive, high-performing teams.",
